# Weather Admin App ğŸŒ¤ï¸

> A comprehensive SMS-based weather information platform with AI assistant integration for Tanzania

[![Android](https://img.shields.io/badge/Android-5.0%2B-green.svg)](https://developer.android.com)
[![Firebase](https://img.shields.io/badge/Firebase-Enabled-orange.svg)](https://firebase.google.com)
