## ğŸ”’ Security

- âœ… Firebase Authentication for admin access
- âœ… API keys stored in code (single admin setup)
- âœ… SMS permissions properly managed
- âœ… Input validation on all SMS commands
- âš ï¸ **Important**: Never commit `google-services.json` to public repos
- âš ï¸ **Important**: Rotate API keys if exposed

