## ğŸ› Troubleshooting

### Build Issues
```bash
./gradlew clean build
```

### SMS Not Sending
- Check SMS permissions in app settings
- Verify device has SMS capability
- Check SIM card is active

### AI Not Responding
- Verify API keys in `AiConfig.java`
- Check internet connection
- Test API key at provider's console
- Select working provider (Groq recommended)

